{"tid":240052,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月新番】 劍姬神聖譚 05","createTime":"2017-05-12T06:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T08:37:14.000Z","uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfbf5a3bfe32db220fb9750ed5e52e13a3579553","tid":240052,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fGRSpYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfGRSpYr.jpg&h=d01488a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正傳只有149句台詞的【劍姬】艾絲&middot;華倫斯坦。<br />\n以最強聞名的女劍士今天也和同伴們一起，<br />\n前往廣大的地下迷宮「地下城」。<br />\n腐朽成灰的龍的殘骸，隱藏於暗處的異常事態<br />\n在種種神秘的威脅來襲的深層域50階層，<br />\n艾絲呼喚疾風，在迷宮的黑暗中刻下一閃！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;之後來訪的是，與少年的「邂逅」<br />\n「那個&hellip;&hellip;你，沒事嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n在迷宮都市歐拉麗之地，<br />\n少女與少年的物語鮮烈地交錯！<br />\n<br />\n這是，另一個眷族的物語，<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;【劍姬神聖譚Sword Oratoria】&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：大森藤ノ<br />\n角色原案：灰村清孝、安田典生<br />\n監督：鈴木洋平<br />\n系列構成：白根秀樹<br />\n角色設計：木本茂樹<br />\n音樂：井內啟二<br />\n動畫製作：J.C.STAFF<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n艾絲&middot;華倫斯坦:大西沙織<br />\n蕾菲亞&middot;維里迪斯:木村珠莉<br />\n蒂奧娜&middot;席呂特:村川梨衣<br />\n蒂奧涅&middot;席呂特:高橋未奈美<br />\n洛基:久保由利香<br />\n芬恩&middot;蒂姆那:田村睦心<br />\n里維莉雅&middot;利歐斯&middot;阿爾弗:川澄綾子(正傳動畫版:種田梨沙)<br />\n貝爾&middot;克朗尼：松岡禎丞<br />\n赫斯緹雅：水瀨祈<br />\nviu逢星期五深夜 03:30更新<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ:外傳跟正傳有何關連<br />\nA:外傳是以【劍姬】和洛基眷族作為主視點的故事,而時間點和正傳是一樣的<br />\nQ:正傳主角會否出場<br />\nA:由於跟正傳是同一時間點,所以同樣會有艾絲和貝爾相會的情節[/quote]op:RE-ILLUSION<br />\n歌：井口裕香<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G868034.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG868034.jpg&h=3bc5cdbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nED:day by day<br />\n歌：鹿乃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w53083Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw53083Q.jpg&h=7e83910a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rS47p5n-jic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrS47p5n-jic&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b484e335\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rS47p5n-jic</a><br />\n 第5話 WEB予告[/quote]"},{"pid":"52c8dec7b36b786c731d7f7fcff2672227513617","tid":240052,"uid":24263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f167083428da4d793cbb67672adebaa219b1f8","tid":240052,"uid":99827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1296.photobucket.com/albums/ag11/cleverchm/QQ20170501184759_zps3xcd5f4s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1296.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fag11%2Fcleverchm%2FQQ20170501184759_zps3xcd5f4s.png&h=cff997cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f72e69625257a9dda60bc5fa2d2d164f18fc79d","tid":240052,"uid":99827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i1296.photobucket.com/albums/ag11/cleverchm/QQ20170501184759_zps3xcd5f4s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1296.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fag11%2Fcleverchm%2FQQ20170501184759_zps3xcd5f4s.png&h=cff997cf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n外傳D插圖真係幾好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44aa149c7f16fe24ace56341a7fb86f41d3097e","tid":240052,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:45:42.000Z","msg":"報到 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/12/164540_70d9c48744e072f0242ef0692d9216d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2F164540_70d9c48744e072f0242ef0692d9216d2.jpg&h=16e5e91e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"313e40ce0af4114663f17b3eac809b0136ec6196","tid":240052,"uid":23473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-